tr_s89Title:
ANJARA AMIN’NY FIVORIANA MOMBA
NY FIAINANTSIKA SY NY FANOMPOANA
tr_s89DescFooter: Ho an’ny mpianatsy: Hita amy Tari-dalana ho An’ny Fiainantsika noho ty Fanompoa loharanon-kevitsy noho ty lesona amy anjaranao. Ampolio dinihy, azafady, ty toromariky mikasiky an'ny anjara iny, sady hazavà amy Toromariky Mahakasiky ty Fiainantsika noho ty Fanompoa (S-38).
tr_publicWitnessing: Fandahara fampiofana fitoria amy pilasy maro olo
tr_lcNoAssignedVariations: Raha Vitan'ny Fandamina|Vaovao Farany Baka amy Filan-kevi-pitantana
tr_exportMidweekMeetinDesc: Filio ty fandahara na taratasy hofenoa teanao hatao Pdf. Filio koa ty modely teanao hampiasà. Ho hajaỳ programa toy mba hampiasànao afara any lafa hanao safidy iha.
tr_applicationAPS: Fangataha hanao ty fanompoan’ny mpisava lala mpanampy
tr_applicationAPSDesc: Tea an’i Jehovah noho ta hanampy ty hafa hianatsy mikasiky azy noho ty sitrapony tena aho, ka maniry hampitombo ty fotoa hanompoako amy faritany eny. Ta ho mpisava lala mpanampy aho amy fotoa voaresaky ambany etoa:
tr_continuousAPS: Ta ho mpisava lala mpanampy avao zisiky hampisy fampandrenesa hafa.
tr_pioneerApplicationMoral: Soa fandaisam-bata aho sady mana fahazara soa. Fa nanao fandahara aho mba hanatratsirako lera takỳ amiko.—Henteo Ty Fanompoantsika Ilay Fanjakana Ziein 2013, p. 2.
tr_noteAPSApplication: FANAMARIHA: Laha azo atao, le alefaso herinandro alohan’ny fotoa teanao hanomboha ty fanompoan’ny mpisava lala mpanampy fangatahana toy, fara fahatarany. Tsy halefa amy biraon’ny sampana any fangataha toy, fe ho hajarỳ anatin'ny taratasin’ny ﬁangona.
tr_attentionServiceCommittee:
Attention Congregation Service committee:

1. Is the applicant a good example in Christian living, being of good moral character?

2. Persons reproved or reinstated during the past year or those who still have restrictions on them do not qualify.

3. Have you consulted with the appropriate group overseer?
tr_moreInformationForAP: Ta ho lasa mpisava lala maharitsy va iha? Fenò fangataha amy <0>hub.jw.org</0> na miresaha amy anti-panahy amy fiangonanareo ao.
tr_hourGoalDesc: Tokony ho 30 lera ro tratsiry laha hanao mpisava lala mpanampy mitohy. Afaky manatratsy 15 lera koa iha amy vola ampandrenesan'ny anti-panahy hoe azo anaova ani-zay.
tr_applicationSubmittedDesc: Hodinihan’ny komitin’ny fanompoa raha io, le hiresaky aminao rozy laha ekè ty fangatahanao
